DESCRIPTION:REVELATOR is a brand new power-house tribute band based in Chi
 cago\, dedicated to honoring the Grammy- winning music of Tedeschi Trucks 
 Band with authenticity\, soul\, and impeccable musicianship. This show aim
 s to recreate every detail from a real TTB performance. Everything from th
 e song arrangements\, music equipment\, visual aesthetics\, and expansive 
 ever-changing catalog will appeal not only to die-hard TTB fans\, but also
  to fans of Chicagos thriving blues and jam band community.The Band:Sophie
  Hafer Lead Vocals \\+ GuitarZach Avery Lead GuitarBrother John Kattke Key
 sJulian Daniell DrumsTodd Lazar BassGracie Lubisky Backing VocalsCaleb Mit
 chell TrumpetJim Schram - Saxophone
