BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Sunny Akhigbe presents: Nourish for Life: A Community Nutrition Ta
 lk
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T140000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T150000
UID:2603036S4AW6WKOk2SkJNX_IDZsQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/7M-KCgYK00yYFk5FH6Alpg.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Wild Onion Market\, in partnership with Sunny Akhigbe of the A
  Boy and His Dream Foundation\, is pleased to present a free community eve
 nt\, Nourish for Life: A Community Nutrition Talk\, on Saturday\, March 1
 4\, from 2 to 3 p.m. \n\nThe presentation will be at Wild Onion Market a 
 community-owned grocery store at 7007 N Clark in Rogers Park.\n\nSunny Akh
 igbe is the founder of A Boy and His Dream\, a 501\\(c\\)\\(3\\) nonprofit
  dedicated to creating opportunities for underserved youth through educati
 on\, mentorship\, nutrition\, and community support\, both locally in Chic
 ago and internationally in Nigeria. He will lead this informative session 
 focused on practical\, accessible approaches to healthy eating.\n\nMr Akhi
 gbe\, a native of Nigeria\, now calls Chicago home. He is a business profe
 ssional with an MBA from Purdue University and also a certified fitness co
 ach. Complementing his philanthropic work\, he is a powerful motivational 
 speaker.\n\nHis talk will explore how to eat well within real-world constr
 aints such as cost\, access\, and time. Topics include selecting wholesome
  foods on a budget and making everyday food choices that support long-term
  health for individuals and families.\n\nThis event is free and open to th
 e public. Attendees will have the opportunity to engage directly with Mr. 
 Akhigbe\, ask questions\, and leave with actionable insights for better no
 urishment and wellbeing.\n\nEvent Details What: Nourish for Life: A Commu
 nity Nutrition Talk with Sunny Akhigbe When: Saturday\, March 14\, 2026\,
  2 to 3 p.m. Where: Wild Onion Market\, 7007 N Clark St.\, Chicago\, IL 6
 0626 Cost: Free\n\nLearn more about A Boy and His Dream at www.aboyandhis
 dream.org\, and about Wild Onion Market at wildonionmarket.com.
LOCATION:Wild Onion Market community grocery store
URL:https://wildonionmarket.com/event/nourish-for-life-a-community-nutriti
 on-talk/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
