 ortalimages/portalimages/i3TZ8z9NUkqlde1s68L6rw.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The Woman's Club of Evanston has been making audiences laugh f
 or a good cause for 70\\+ years with its annual Revue. Join us for an even
 ing of entertaining parody songs poking fun at current and timeless topics
 . We are excited to have Piven Theatre Workshop as the 2026 Revue Benefic
 iary. Piven's mission encourages creative exploration while celebrating ea
 ch individual's unique voice. Proceeds will support expanding Piven's prog
 ramming for the community.
LOCATION:Woman's Club of Evanston Ballroom
URL:http://wcofe.org
