DESCRIPTION:Suzanne B. Calder Community Stakeholders Panel Discussion﻿: 
 Building a Bridge of Justice Between Environmental Sustainability and Affo
 rdable Housing benefiting Connections for the Homeless.\n\nHow can we adva
 nce both affordable housing and climate resilience? And how can we ensure 
 sustainability policies protect\, rather than burden\, communities most vu
 lnerable to climate change?\n\nJoin the free community conversation follow
 ing the Inspire luncheon at 1:45 - 2:30 PM on Thursday\, March 19 on the f
 irst floor of the Woman's Club of Evanston \\(1702 Chicago Ave\\).
