SUMMARY:Solstice: A Winter Circus Experience
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T190000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T190000
UID:260314MAHi5i3YKkuivoLo1GCBrQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/knBnJq6YAUSpuelt1cA4fw.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Step into a dreamscape with Solstice: a Winter Circus Experien
 ce. At the heart of the story is a girl who loses her light and stumbles i
 nto a world where time bends\, memories breathe\, and the familiar becomes
  impossibly strange. Shadows dance\, snow drifts fall\, and acrobats blur 
 the line between the everyday and the extraordinary. More than a circus\, 
 "Solstice" is a living poem ? a place where nostalgia meets surreal wonder
 \, and where audiences are invited to rediscover the childlike awe of seei
 ng snow for the first time! In 2026\, Solstice returns with all-new elemen
 ts and an original score composed by NC artist Bella Nona\, weaving music\
 , movement\, and imagination into a one-of-a-kind celebration of the human
  spirit.
LOCATION:Northlight Theatre
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=
 5#/details/solstice-a-winter-circus-experience/17366253/2026-03-22T19
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
