 ths old to participate and wearing current rabies tags. Both hunts will ta
 ke place at the same time on different fields.  After the event make sure 
 to grab a picture with the Easter Bunny! Please bring your own bag or bask
 et.  Please note\, this hunt is specifically for dogs. Handlers may guide 
 dogs to eggs\, but must not hunt for eggs on their own. Fee is per dog. Bu
 nny Brunch and Children's Egg Hunt Information: https://wilmettepark.org/e
 vent-list/bunny-brunch-egg-hunts
