BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:5th-8th Grade Caregiver Sex Education Workshop: It's That Easy
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T180000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T193000
UID:250923l49b8GieqEuUcoNgJOEcNw
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/dUYMqomzuEeEX9EFRDZQCw.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The "It's That Easy:" Caregiver Sex Ed Learning Session is pre
 sented by YWCA/Evanston North Shore and Evanston School District 65. This
  virtual workshop is free for all to attend\, but registration is necessar
 y so the facilitator can plan accordingly.\n\nSession Description:\n\nThis
  workshop is for parents\, caregivers\, and family members who want to dee
 pen their knowledge about healthy sexual development\, sexual identity\, a
 nd relationships and how to discuss these topics with their children and t
 eens. Participate in a little bit of sex ed while your students receive it
  in school!\n\nLed by Hallie Cohen\, Training and Prevention Coordinator f
 or YWCA Evanston/North Shore and sex education consultant to D65\, this wo
 rkshop will be an engaging\, interactive\, and discussion-based. During th
 is workshop\, participants will:\n\n- Explain how their own experience wit
 h sexuality education impacts how and what they share with their own child
 ren\;\n\n- Identify the most important values and messages they would like
  to pass on to their children about sexuality\;\n\n- Gain an understanding
  of healthy sexual development for their child’s age range\;\n\n- Identi
 fy teachable moments during which they can share information and family va
 lues regarding sexuality.\n\nThis workshop will be held twice\, with the f
 ocus being on different age groups. If you are unable to attend the date w
 ith the ideal focus for you\, feel free to register for the other date. Yo
 u will surely get a lot out of it\, and some of the material will be the s
 ame.\n\n- Tuesday\, March 10\, 6-7:30 pm – \\(caregivers of\\) preK-4th 
 grade\n\n- Tuesday\, March 24\, 6-7:30 pm - \\(caregivers of\\) 5th-8th gr
 ade\n\nPlease direct any additional questions to Hallie Cohen - hcohen@ywc
 a-ens.org\n\nYou do not need to be a D65 family to attend\, this event is 
 open to all!
LOCATION:YWCA Evanston North/Shore
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=
 5#/details/5th-8th-grade-caregiver-sex-education-workshop-it-s-that-easy/1
 6932400/2026-03-24T18
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
