 ortalimages/portalimages/31Ug2cCI4Eui7PpXNizPtQ.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Zora’s Place for a powerful evening of poetry and
  reflection with local poet The Honorable Angelina Nordstrom.\n\nRooted in
  lived experience and spiritual reflection\, Angelina’s work explores wh
 at it means to move through the world holding multiple identities while re
 claiming power\, voice\, and wholeness.\n\nThis gathering is an invitation
  to listen\, witness\, and celebrate the beauty of authenticity\, resilien
 ce\, and transformation. Angelina will read from their poetry collection\,
  DOUBLE SPIRIT: The Inner Union of the Sacred Feminine & the Divine Mascu
 line Identities.\n\nEvent Details\n\n• Doors open at 6:45 PM\n\n• Poet
 ry reading begins at 7:00 PM\n\n• Audience Q&A to follow\n\n• Books wi
 ll be available for purchase at the event
