 ay\\) ⏰ Time: 10:30 a.m. 📍 Location: First Presbyterian Church of Eva
 nston 1427 Chicago Ave\, Evanston\, IL 60201 \\[firstprese...anston.org\\]
 \n\nFamilies are especially welcome. Children are invited to worship along
 side their parents\, and after the service we’ll host a fun Easter egg h
 unt along with a special photo backdrop for all ages.\n\nAccessibility: Ac
 cessible entrances and on-site parking are available\, with additional str
 eet parking nearby.\n\nWhether you’ve been part of a church for years or
  you’re exploring faith for the first time\, there’s a place for you h
 ere. All ages and backgrounds are welcome. \\[firstprese...anston.org\\]\n
 \nLearn more: https://firstpresevanston.org/event/easter-sunday-worship/
