 \\+ student  information session in the Welcome Center\, Room E112 as we d
 iscuss these t opics. This information session will be focused on incoming
  freshmen\, stud ents who are new to ETHS\, interested current ETHS studen
 ts who identify as  LGBTQ\\+\, and their families. The purpose of this ses
 sion is to help incomi ng and new students navigate ETHS for an affirming 
 school year.For additio nal information regarding Supports for Transgender
  and Gender Expansive St udents reference the ETHS website. If you would l
 ike to develop a gender s upport plan\, please begin by completing the Stu
 dent Advocacy Form \\(https:/ /www.eths.k12.il.us/Page/1355\\).
