ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/OY2WVMOEO0q51qe0_Ksm8A.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The Evanston Art Center \\(EAC\\) is excited to welcome the pu
 blic to our upcoming exhibition\, Joan Ruppert | Making the Cut. The exhib
 ition will be on display from March 28 - April 26\, 2026\, with an opening
  reception on Sunday\, March 29\, from 1–4pm that will be free and open 
 to the public.\n\nJoan Tortorici Ruppert is a television producer and medi
 a content creator based in Glenview\, IL. Her exhibition Making the Cut sh
 owcases live-action collages that combine characters from her late father
 ’s vintage negatives together with contemporary environments. Each new c
 ollage is organic\, unpredictable\, and unrepeatable\, disrupting time and
  space to write new chapters in her family’s story.
LOCATION:Evanston Art Center
URL:https://www.evanstonartcenter.org/exhibitions/joan-ruppert-making-cut
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
